,0.052674,0.039922]},{"section":5,"text":"They're also limited to the right side of his head, which makes me think it's not a migraine that typically affects one side but can sometimes be unilateral.","dimension":5,"group":4,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.072399,0.098229,0.1026,0.10069,0.095121,0.091734,0.089374,0.084856,0.079232,0.072995,0.063632,0.049144],"unified_progress":[0.069839,0.089663,0.095901,0.096704,0.096106,0.097444,0.091413,0.091872,0.083532,0.078222,0.063611,0.045691]},{"section":6,"text":"He also mentions associated tearing and reddening of the right eye, along with nasal stuffiness.","dimension":9,"group":5,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.063984,0.12448,0.11426,0.11078,0.09488,0.08921,0.087503,0.077821,0.069184,0.062018,0.057031,0.048856],"unified_progress":[0.078799,0.11364,0.10289,0.098865,0.093974,0.092524,0.084949,0.086103,0.079126,0.067417,0.056787,0.044932]},{"section":7,"text":"Tearing and redness in one eye could point towards something related to the eye itself, maybe a sinus issue or something more serious like an aneurysm.","dimension":3,"group":6,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.041964,0.07405,0.095788,0.1169,0.10402,0.099859,0.1005,0.091609,0.082587,0.082845,0.06216,0.04772],"unified_progress":[0.041059,0.077426,0.098,0.11213,0.10453,0.099717,0.10128,0.094308,0.087457,0.07978,0.062593,0.041725]},{"section":8,"text":"The stuffiness in the nose makes me think of sinusitis, which often causes pressure and congestion.","dimension":3,"group":6,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.05186,0.070178,0.083584,0.092922,0.097223,0.099052,0.10024,0.096342,0.09101,0.084842,0.072536,0.060207],"unified_progress":[0.052214,0.074412,0.08686,0.09358,0.098208,0.09973,0.097857,0.096429,0.090682,0.0845,0.071112,0.054415]},{"section":9,"text":"The neurological examination is normal, so that rules out some of the more concerning neurological issues.","dimension":5,"group":4,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.028544,0.0