 the \"cluster headache triad\" when these symptoms occur together.","dimension":2,"group":3,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.035098,0.04517,0.060776,0.07252,0.088405,0.098595,0.10549,0.11268,0.11266,0.10131,0.087849,0.079443],"unified_progress":[0.034941,0.053929,0.074472,0.086817,0.09407,0.10365,0.10472,0.1048,0.10076,0.0971,0.080057,0.064681]},{"section":15,"text":"I should also consider other possibilities, like sinus headaches or migraines, but cluster headaches fit better here because of the timing and the associated eye symptoms.","dimension":5,"group":4,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.032418,0.049758,0.061887,0.070686,0.07732,0.08474,0.091919,0.099681,0.10554,0.11124,0.11016,0.10465],"unified_progress":[0.031335,0.053151,0.067168,0.07832,0.084939,0.089772,0.093224,0.099184,0.10002,0.10485,0.10103,0.097013]},{"section":16,"text":"Sinus headaches usually come on with sinus pressure, but the tearing and redness are more aligned with cluster headaches.","dimension":5,"group":4,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.037314,0.043696,0.059468,0.069697,0.081524,0.091554,0.098561,0.10772,0.1125,0.1093,0.10226,0.086406],"unified_progress":[0.0366,0.053934,0.069507,0.079592,0.088904,0.096428,0.099203,0.10395,0.10328,0.10433,0.091502,0.072769]},{"section":17,"text":"Migraines can be severe and unilateral, but they often have other symptoms like nausea or aura, which aren't mentioned here.","dimension":5,"group":4,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.023815,0.043651,0.062947,0.073304,0.082622,0.092676,0.10022,0.11092,0.11583,0.1151,0.1063,0.072607],"unified_progress":[0.027314,0.051561,0.06864,0.079065,0.09074,0.096321,0.10187,0.10897,0.10877,0.11583,0.091951,0.058975]},{"section":18,"text":"So, the most likely diagnosis is cluster headache. ...","dimension":4,"group":0,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.023566,0.045143,0.050644,0.05713,0.060457,0.065852,0.075821,0.082661,0.094385,0.11233,0.14,0.19201],"unified_progress":[0.019502,0.0391